                    alt="SEO audit and technical analysis dashboard" 
                    class="w-full h-44 object-cover shadow-lg"
                    style="opacity: 1 !important; filter: none !important; background: #000 !important; display: block; position: relative; z-index: 1000;"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Successful SEO optimization begins with comprehensive site analysis, identifying technical issues, content gaps, and competitive opportunities. Professional SEO consultants conduct detailed keyword research, competitor analysis, and site performance benchmarking to establish baseline metrics and optimization potential across all digital touchpoints.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                The audit phase typically reveals that websites operate with 40-70% untapped SEO potential, 20-35% technical issues requiring immediate attention, and 15-25% content optimization opportunities for improved rankings. This analysis forms the foundation for strategic SEO roadmaps that prioritize high-impact, measurable improvements while building toward comprehensive search optimization.
              </p>

              <!-- SEO Implementation Approach -->
